          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>The Borderlands series' iconic cel-shaded visual style is one of its defining characteristics, perfectly matching the goofy humor and absurd violence the games are known for. The upcoming Borderlands 4 will introduce fans to an all-new side of this stylish sci-fi universe with its own unique locations, weapons, and characters. If you're eager to see how the visuals of the fourth entry evolved during development, you'll want to check out the upcoming <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1506748406?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Art of Borderlands 4</a>, releasing September 30. Preorders for the 224-page hardcover book are available for $54.41 at Amazon.</p><p>The Art of Borderlands 4 is just one of many Borderlands books that are available now or up for preorder. Here's a quick look at all of the Borderlands books you can buy or preorder now. Below the list, you can take an in-depth look at the upcoming Borderlands 4 art book, the new graphic novel, a prose novel by the writer behind Borderlands 2, and more. Borderlands 4 launches on PC and consoles on September 23, and while the game is not yet available to preorder, these new books and graphic novels should keep fans busy in the meantime.</p><h2 dir="ltr">Borderlands books</h2><h3 dir="ltr">Artbooks and coloring books</h3><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1506748406?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Art of Borderlands 4</a> -- $54.41 (<del>$55</del>) | Releases September 30</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Art-Borderlands-3-Insight-Editions/dp/1683835719?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Art of Borderlands 3</a> -- $23 (<del>$45</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Worlds-Borderlands-Rick-Barba/dp/1506720498?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Worlds of Borderlands</a><span> --</span><span> </span><span>$20 (</span><del>$30</del><span>)</span></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-Official-Coloring-Elmer-Damasco/dp/B0DV4NJDD4?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: The Official Coloring Book</a> -- $15 | Releases September 9</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Art-Tiny-Tinas-Wonderlands/dp/1506734529?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">The Art of Tiny Tina's Wonderlands</a><span> -- $28 (</span><del>$50</del><span>)</span></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Tiny-Tinas-Wonderlands-Badasses-Adventure/dp/B0CTYGLYD8?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Tiny Tina's Wonderlands: A Bunkers &amp; Badasses Coloring Adventure</a> -- $12.60 (<del>$15</del>)</li></ul><h3 dir="ltr">Novels and comics</h3><ul><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-Mysterious-Memento-Amy-Chu/dp/1506745350?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: Moxxi's Mysterious Memento (Graphic Novel)</a> -- $20 | Releases September 2</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Tiny-Tinas-Wonderlands-Land-Giants/dp/1506745164?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Tiny Tina's Wonderlands: Land of the Giants (Graphic Novel)</a><span> -- $18.59 (</span><del>$20</del><span>)</span></li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-Debt-Alive-Anthony-Burch/dp/1803363533?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: Debt or Alive (Paperback)</a> -- $16 (<del>$17</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1439198470?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: The Fallen (Book 1) Paperback</a> -- $17.49 (<del>$22</del>)</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-2-Unconquered-John-Shirley-ebook/dp/B006VJMYRG?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: Unconquered (Book 2) Kindle</a> -- $3</li><li dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1439198497?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Boderlands Gunsight (Book 3) Paperback</a> -- $15 (<del>$20</del>)</li></ul><h3 dir="ltr">Cookbook</h3><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Eat-Borderlands-Culinary-Through-Pandora/dp/B0DL4H9T83?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Eat the Borderlands: One Loader Bot's Culinary Tour Through Pandora and Beyond!</a> -- $28 (<del>$30</del>) | Releases July 29</li></ul><div title="6531707 - The Art of Borderlands 4 and more Borderlands books" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3557" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6531707 - The Art of Borderlands 4 and more Borderlands books" data-collection="">                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-Debt-Alive-Anthony-Burch/dp/1803363533?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Borderlands-Debt-Alive-Anthony-Burch\/dp\/1803363533?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-Debt-Alive-Anthony-Burch/dp/1803363533?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Borderlands: Debt or Alive</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-Debt-Alive-Anthony-Burch/dp/1803363533?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Borderlands-Debt-Alive-Anthony-Burch\/dp\/1803363533?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-Debt-Alive-Anthony-Burch/dp/1803363533?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$16 (was $17)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>While most of the stuff listed above won't be out for a short while, you can grab some other Borderlands books right now. Last year saw the release of the novel Borderlands: Debt or Alive, a new adventure starring Tales From the Borderlands' Fiona and Sasha. What makes this one notable is that it's written by Anthony Burch, the writer behind Borderlands 2. The first Borderlands sequel is still a beloved game in the series, and its storyline is widely regarded to be the best.</p><p>You can also check out three books that were released shortly after Borderlands 2 launched. This three-book series focused on three of the Vault Hunters from the first Borderlands sequel--Roland, Brick, and Mordecai--and the adventures they got up to on the planet of Pandora.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1439198470?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: The Fallen</a> -- $17.49 (<del>$22</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Borderlands-2-Unconquered-John-Shirley-ebook/dp/B006VJMYRG?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: Unconquered (Kindle edition)</a> -- $3.44</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1439198497?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Borderlands: Gunsight</a> -- $15 (<del>$20</del>)</li></ul></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Worlds-Borderlands-Rick-Barba/dp/1506720498?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Worlds-Borderlands-Rick-Barba\/dp\/1506720498?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Worlds-Borderlands-Rick-Barba/dp/1506720498?tag=gamespot-promos-20">The World of Borderlands</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Worlds-Borderlands-Rick-Barba/dp/1506720498?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Worlds-Borderlands-Rick-Barba\/dp\/1506720498?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Worlds-Borderlands-Rick-Barba/dp/1506720498?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$20 (was $30)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>The World of Borderlands is the go-to guide for anyone planning to visit Pandora. Inside this 208-page tome you'll find a comprehensive guide on everything you have to watch out for on that alien planet, like bloodthirsty beasts, rampaging bandits, and worst of all, out-of-control corporations.</p>                      </div>                                                                        </div><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/super-mario-bros-1993-movie-30th-anniversary-edition-blu-ray-where-to-watch-buy-amazon/1100-6531622/">Highly Limited Super Mario Bros. 30th Anniversary 4K Blu-Ray In Stock At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-board-game-monkey-palace-strategy-building-set-amazon-deal-2025/1100-6528660/">Lego Monkey Palace Board Game Is Over 50% Off At Amazon Right Now</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/8bitdo-leverless-arcade-controller-xbox-switch-2-pc-preorder-amazon/1100-6531585/">8BitDo Reveals Leverless Arcade Controllers For PC, Switch, And Xbox</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/locke-key-keyhouse-comic-compendium-gets-massive-limited-time-discount/1100-6531565/">Locke &amp; Key Keyhouse Comic Compendium Gets Massive Limited-Time Discount</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-mario-kart-mario-standard-kart-review-where-to-buy/1100-6530000/">Lego's Awesome New Mario Kart Display Set Is Available Now</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/joe-abercrombie-the-devils-new-fantasy-book-series-2025-amazon/1100-6531472/">First Book In Joe Abercrombie's New Fantasy Series Is Finally Here</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/transformers-optimus-prime-lego-set-restocked-and-20-off-at-amazon/1100-6509331/">Amazon Restocks Lego Transformers Optimus Prime, Offers Big Discount</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-super-mario-bowser-muscle-car-amazon-deal-retiring-lego-set/1100-6531375/">PSA: Lego Bowser's Muscle Car Is Retiring - Save Big On 3 Mario Sets Before They're Gone</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
